# Install  new doc structure

This file is used to create the new doc structure for docusaurus based on the old docs/INSTALL.md file.

The new files will be created in the ./website/docs/getting-started directory.

Below, each section will be a file in the ./website/docs/getting-started directory, and the content will be the content of the section in the old docs/INSTALL.md file, listed in the section contents.

## first-steps.md:

- [First Steps](#first-steps)
  - [Quick Start Checklist](#quick-start-checklist)
  - [Accessing the Dashboard](#accessing-the-dashboard)
  - [Initial Setup](#initial-setup)
    - [1. Verify Installation](#1-verify-installation)
    - [2. Configure Your First Duplicati Server](#2-configure-your-first-duplicati-server)
    - [3. Basic Configuration](#3-basic-configuration)
      - [Server Settings](#server-settings)
      - [Display Settings](#display-settings)
  - [Understanding the Dashboard](#understanding-the-dashboard)
    - [Dashboard Overview](#dashboard-overview)
    - [Key Features](#key-features)
  - [Common Tasks](#common-tasks)
    - [Adding a New Server](#adding-a-new-server)
    - [Setting Up Notifications](#setting-up-notifications)
    - [Monitoring Backups](#monitoring-backups)
  - [Troubleshooting](#troubleshooting)
    - [Dashboard Not Loading](#dashboard-not-loading)
    - [No Backup Data](#no-backup-data)
    - [Notifications Not Working](#notifications-not-working)
  - [Getting Help](#getting-help)
    - [Documentation](#documentation)
    - [Support](#support)
  - [Next Steps](#next-steps)
  - [Tips for Success](#tips-for-success)

